The paper focuses on visualizing spreadsheet content for analytic insight and validation, which falls under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Additionally, the paper deals with data visualization and manipulation, which could be categorized under databases (cs.DB) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also discusses the layout and formatting of the spreadsheet, which could be considered under graphics (cs.GR) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
